&lt;p&gt;BeyondTrust is a place where you can bring your purpose to life through the work that you do, creating a safer world through our cybersecurity SaaS portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our culture of flexibility, trust, and continual learning means you will be recognized for your growth, and for the impact you make on our success. You will be surrounded by people who challenge, support, and inspire you to be the best version of yourself.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;The Role&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;BeyondTrust is the worldwide leader in intelligent identity and access security, empowering organizations to protect identities, stop threats, and securely deliver dynamic access. Our industry-leading platform and integrated products offer the most advanced Privileged Access Management (PAM) and Cloud Infrastructure Entitlements Management (CIEM)&amp;nbsp;solutions, enabling enterprises to reduce their attack surface across traditional, cloud, and hybrid environments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Entitle,&amp;nbsp;BeyondTrust’s&amp;nbsp;industry leading&amp;nbsp;product&amp;nbsp;offering provides granular, just‑in‑time access&amp;nbsp;and advanced permission management&amp;nbsp;across cloud infrastructure, SaaS, and modern enterprise environments. As part of our vision to become the modern standard for identity security in multi‑cloud infrastructure, we are accelerating toward a future where secure access&amp;nbsp;for humans and machines&amp;nbsp;is automated, intelligent, and increasingly free of human‑managed processes.&amp;nbsp;We place a heavy emphasis on building products that address&amp;nbsp;our&amp;nbsp;customers&#39;&amp;nbsp;modern&amp;nbsp;pain points,&amp;nbsp;making security&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;compliance a low-effort activity.&amp;nbsp;We value technical curiosity and proactive learning. The ideal PM keeps pace with the market and technology changes, understands the implications, and helps to craft roadmaps&amp;nbsp;that deliver outcomes in support of our customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;As a Senior Product Manager for&amp;nbsp;Entitle, you will&amp;nbsp;be a&amp;nbsp;major stakeholder&amp;nbsp;in&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;product strategy and&amp;nbsp;lead the&amp;nbsp;execution across a cross-functional team. You will collaborate with leadership to shape the long-term vision, partner closely with engineering and design, and own delivery of platform-wide capabilities that scale with our rapidly growing user base.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop, execute, and maintain an agile product, roadmap and craft user stories with the broader product management team as a core part of BeyondTrust’s identity security portfolio.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and prioritize features for visibility, permission management, least privilege, compliance automation, and identity governance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee the full product lifecycle from concept through launch and performance measurement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion user needs through AI-driven insights, research, and continuous delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate customer, market, and business requirements into actionable roadmaps and measurable outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with engineering to deliver secure, technically sound products aligned with best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor industry trends and competitors to inform product direction and strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the shift to probabilistic product experiences, balancing user experience with security and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support sales and pre-sales activities, and gather feedback from internal and external stakeholders to refine enhancements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;What You’ll Bring&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-reliant leader and team player, with a “let’s do this” approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree in Computer Science, Information Systems, Engineering, Business, or related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of proven product management experience in identity management or security SaaS platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with PM AI tools, LLM prototyping and prompt engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in the modern AI stack, demonstrable experience building or integrating AI/ML-powered features.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical background in Identity Security, Identity Access Management, Privileged Access Management, Identity Threat Detection and Response, Cloud Infrastructure, Cloud Security Management, Cloud Infrastructure Entitlements Management, or related discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relevant military experience is considered an advantage.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;public cloud computing, e.g. Azure, AWS, Google Cloud Platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Agile methodologies and&amp;nbsp;a track record&amp;nbsp;of delivering results in a fast-paced environment, specifically within the Software Development Lifecycle (SDLC)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent written, verbal, and presentation English communication skills, effectively contributing within an international corporate setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates strong organizational skills by effectively multitasking and prioritizing responsibilities, maintains a professional demeanor at all times, and consistently supports and adheres to the Company’s Core Values.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a passion for design and good UX&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to travel (not often, but we would need someone open to it when or if it is ever needed)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;Better Together&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Diversity. Inclusion. They’re more than just words for us. They are the guiding values of how we build our teams, cultivate leaders, and create a culture where people feel connected.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We take care of our employees so they can take care of our customers. Customers who&amp;nbsp;come from all walks of life just like us. We hire incredible people from diverse backgrounds because when we are different together, we are stronger together.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;About Us&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BeyondTrust is the global identity security leader protecting Paths to Privilege™. Our identity-centric approach goes beyond securing privileges and access, empowering organizations with the most effective solution to manage the entire identity attack surface and neutralize threats, whether from external attacks or insiders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BeyondTrust is leading the charge in transforming identity security to prevent breaches and limit the blast radius of attacks, while creating a superior customer experience and operational efficiencies. We are trusted by 20,000 customers, including 75 of the Fortune 100, and our global ecosystem of partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Learn more at &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.beyondtrust.com/&quot;&gt;www.beyondtrust.com&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
